        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 19. Septembopyrina tozeumaophila n. sp., holotype female (CIEHI790502a) (A–K): A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Right antenna and antennule. D. Right maxilliped, external view. E. Right side of barbula. F. Right oostegite 1, external view. G. Right oostegite 1, internal view. H. Left oostegite 1, external view. I. Left oostegite 1, internal view. J. Right pereopod 1. K. Right pereopod 7. Allotype male (CIEHI790502b) (L, M): L. Dorsal view. M. Ventral view. Scale: 2 mm (A, B); 0.25 mm (C); 0.5 mm (D– K); 0.6 mm (L, M)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4612568/files/figure.png" .
